author: cbs8
title: TraveLynx taps SuperShuttle International® to partner on transportation services from Orlando to Port Canaveral
text:
SuperShuttle International
ORLANDO, Fla. , Sept. 29, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Stylus Transportation's TraveLynx, a leading providing of ground transportation in central Florida , has tapped SuperShuttle to provide shared-ride services between Orlando International Airport (MCO) and Port Canaveral cruise terminals effective October 1 , 2015. The new service to surrounding area hotels will be served through the recent acquisition of TraveLynx.
Port Canaveral announced an increase in cruise travel starting November of 2015. Rates are $35 per person one-way or $60 per person round-trip, representing a saving of up to 75 percent for travelers. Through this partnership, SuperShuttle will provide share-ride service in its iconic Blue vans as well as its ExecuCar service featuring private town car and SUV service. Stylus, via their TraveLynx division, will provide shared-ride shuttle, motorcoach and mini bus services between MCO and Port Canaveral.
To book a trip, visit http://groups.supershuttle.com/stylus.html . Airport transfers booked online or the SuperShuttle mobile app are eligible to earn airline miles or points through participating loyalty programs including American Airlines AAdvantage®, Delta Air Lines SkyMiles®, Frontier Airlines EarlyReturns®, Southwest Airlines Rapid Rewards® and United Airlines Mileage Plus®.
About Stylus Transportation and TraveLynx
Stylus Transportation has been in business since the early 90's and incorporated in 1996, committed to serving as a reliable and economical means of transportation for all group sizes. With the Stylus brand representing their charter services and the TraveLynx brand representing their shuttle services, the company offers a state-of-the-art fleet of vehicles and broad range of services to locations across the US and Canada . Stylus and TraveLynx provide the customer service, comfort and amenities necessary to ensure your trip becomes a memorable experience. For more information about Stylus, visit www.stylusbus.com .
About SuperShuttle
SuperShuttle, based in Phoenix , is a division of Transdev On Demand. Carrying more than 10 million passengers a year, SuperShuttle is available at over 45 airports in the U.S. and international locations including Paris , London and Cancun and Los Cabos, Mexico . SuperShuttle also provides ExecuCar sedan services at all airports served by SuperShuttle including Los Angeles (LAX), New York (LGA, JFK & EWR), Dallas (DAL & DFW), Washington, D.C. (DCA & IAD) and San Francisco (SFO).
About Transdev On Demand, Inc.
Transdev On Demand, Inc., a division of Phoenix -based Transdev, consists of SuperShuttle International, ExecuCar, Yellow Cab and other national taxi brands. Transdev On Demand, Inc. serves over 80 airports with its multiple services in the on demand service space and has various partnerships with leading airlines and travel wholesalers. Its fleet consists of fuel-efficient vehicles that utilize propane and compressed natural gas.
